text: Ic <on> <siþe> seah //S// //R// //O// //H// hygewloncne, heafodbeorhtne, <swiftne> ofer sælwong swiþe þrægan.
Hæfde him on hrycge hildeþryþe //N// //O// //M// nægledne rad  //A// //G// //E// //W//.
Widlast ferede rynestrong on rade rofne //C// //O// //F// //O// //A// //H//.
For wæs þy beorhtre, swylcra siþfæt.
